\name
sendmsg - send a private persistent message
\synopsis
sendmsg <user> <message>
\description
Allows you to send a private persistent message to anyone.
If the recipient is connected, he'll have the message immediatly or at his next connection to the server.
\example
> sendmsg franck Hey you, dont help them to bury the light
\see also
showmsg, clearmsg
